    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Scout-Nin Keyword: Specialized </p><p>When you would remove a condition on a creature, you can expend a superiority die.</p><p> Until the end of your next turn, you retain the knowledge of how to inflict that condition, and the next time you would deal damage to a creature within this duration, you also inflict one target creature with a number of stacks of the condition equal to a roll of your superiority die, up to its maximum number of stacks.</p><p> You cannot inflict any ranks of exhaustion, slowed, or weakened with this maneuver.</p><p></p>",
